-- China's Net Crude Oil Imports May Increase to 310 Million Tons in 2015
-- B y   B l o o m b e r g   N e w s
-- 2010-10-20T03:32:18Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-10-20/china-s-net-crude-oil-imports-may-increase-to-310-million-tons-in-2015.html
China’s net crude oil imports may
reach 310 million metric tons in 2015, Zhang Fuqin, the bureau
chief of PetroChina’s Planning and Engineering Institute, said
at a conference in Beijing today.  To contact the reporter on this story:
